See [`tf.control_dependencies`](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/framework/utility_functions#control_dependencies) linked there and the link to [`Graph.control_dependencies`](https://www.tensorflow.org/api_docs/python/framework/core_graph_data_structures#Graph.control_dependencies) from it.

